玛格特·罗比在《美国恐怖故事：庇护》的试镜中失败https://www.nme.com/news/tv/margot-robbie-had-failed-audition-for-american-horror-story-asylum-3488663?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=margot-robbie-had-failed-美国恐怖故事庇护试镜Chris EdwardsFri, 25 Aug 2023 13:58:10 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsAmerican Horror StoryBarbiemargot robbie https://www.nme.com/?p=3488663 <p><img width="2192" height="1376" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie.jpg 2192w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-400x251.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-800x502.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-696x437.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-1392x874.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-1068x670.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2192px) 100vw, 2192px" /></p><p> “这太疯狂了，当她走进房间时，她的明星魅力”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/margot-robbie-had-failed-audition-for-american-horror-story-asylum-3488663">玛格特·罗比在《美国恐怖故事：庇护》试镜中失败的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2192" height="1376" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie.jpg 2192w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-400x251.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-800x502.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-696x437.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-1392x874.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Margot-Robbie-1068x670.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2192px) 100vw, 2192px" /></p><p>据透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>在<em>《美国恐怖故事：庇护》</em>的试镜中失败了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<em>Backstage</em>采访时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/american-horror-story"><em>《美国恐怖故事》</em></a>选角总监埃里克·道森 (Eric Dawson) 表示，罗比试镜一个未知角色——许多粉丝认为是莉齐·布罗切尔 (Lizzie Brochere) 饰演的格蕾丝 (Grace)——是他有史以来最喜欢的试镜之一。</p><p> “玛戈特有很多‘it’因素。对于不再与演员共处一室的选角导演来说，这是一件困难的事情，”道森说。</p><p> “玛戈特可能是我有史以来最喜欢的试镜之一，那是在她爆发之前。她真是一位明星。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这太疯狂了，当她走进房间时，她的明星魅力。尽管她没有得到这个角色，但作为选角导演，你要做的事情之一就是：这是一个明星，我们该怎么处理她？</p><p> “不过，她很快就脱离了我们雇用的范围。但这确实是选角过程中有趣的部分，就是看到那些事业刚刚上升的人，”他补充道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3368096" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3368096" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3368096" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1.jpg" alt="芭比玛格特·罗比" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/margot-robbie-barbie-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3368096" class="wp-caption-text">玛格特·罗比饰演芭比娃娃（图片来源：华纳兄弟）</figcaption></figure><p>此后，罗比凭借格蕾塔·葛韦格<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">(Greta Gerwig)</a>饰演的芭比娃娃 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>Barbie)</em></a>登上了全新的明星地位，该片打破了多项票房记录，最近还成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-has-hit-1billion-at-the-global-box-office-3478941#:~:text=Barbie%20has%20hit%20the%20%241,two%20weeks%20after%20its%20release.&amp;text=Greta%20Gerwig's%20film%20is,solely%20directed%20by%20a%20woman.">第一部全球票房收入 10 亿美元的单人女导演电影</a>。</p><p>这位明星还联合制作了这部讽刺喜剧， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-how-much-margot-robbie-will-earn-from-barbie-3483294">预计该片的收入约为 5000 万美元（3920 万英镑）</a> 。</p><p>然而，最近有消息透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-wasnt-first-choice-for-barbie-3482022">罗比实际上并不是主角的首选</a>。在接受<a href="https://www.vogue.com/article/margot-robbie-barbie-summer-cover-2023-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Vogue》</em></a>杂志采访时，这位演员表示，她和导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>最初都希望<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gal-gadot">盖尔·加朵</a>扮演芭比娃娃，但档期冲突阻碍了这一进程。</p><p> “盖尔·加朵是芭比的能量。因为盖尔·加朵是如此美丽得令人难以置信，但你不会因为她那么美丽而讨厌她，因为她是如此真诚，她是如此热情善良，这几乎是愚蠢的。就像在成为傻瓜之前一样，”她说。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/margot-robbie-had-failed-audition-for-american-horror-story-asylum-3488663">玛格特·罗比在《美国恐怖故事：庇护》试镜中失败的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
